  "text": "DNA extraction and purification. Each strain used for probe preparation was grown in 200 to 1,000 ml of GAM medium (Nissui). The anaerobic techniques used were as described previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . High-molecular-weight DNA was isolated by the method of Saito and Miura [CITATION_4] .",
